{"tid":275521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗著住Addidas賣Nike廣告係咩玩法","createTime":"2017-06-08T05:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T05:51:50.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3f482602b8480c8da5b487af9f57be38512ea11","tid":275521,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7%202017-06-06%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.17.55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7%25202017-06-06%2520%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.17.55.png&h=2aa32851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/Cristiano%20Ronaldo%20nin%CC%83o_1_637x390_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2FCristiano%2520Ronaldo%2520nin%25CC%2583o_1_637x390_1.jpg&h=9bb5253c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC朗於上週末代表皇馬贏得連續2年的歐聯冠軍，Nike隨即將C朗拿度的兒時玉照張貼於Instagram作為廣告，指「Nobody believed a boy from Madeira would make it to the stars. Except the boy form Madeira」，為Nike賣廣告。廣告本來非常正路，看似沒有什麼特別之處。誰不知網友突然找出原圖，指當時C朗身穿的衣服是屬於Adidas的衛衣。   長久以來為Nike代言的C朗，今次的兒時照片，被網友貼上更大畫面的原照指出，原照中兒時C朗正穿著Nike競爭對手Adidas衛衣，看來Nike裁剪照片後當作廣告之用。但一看上週末歐聯，就能夠理解的事實是，歐聯決賽兩隊皇家馬德里、祖雲達斯都是Adidas所贊助的隊伍，而歐聯贊助商亦都是來自德國的Adidas。因此惹來網上留言懷疑Nike此舉是有心還是無意，暫時未見雙方就廣告照片使用上有回應。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-06-2017/38330?google_editors_picks=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-06-2017%2F38330%3Fgoogle_editors_picks%3Dtrue&d=Q2Uo%2BPiB9%2B0hyObms5P5V8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4e8b5041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-06-2017/38330?google_editors_picks=true</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017"},{"pid":"ba637a39ca2dd81630fbc63528f716c9100cf4f7","tid":275521,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"蘋果早幾日報左啦 乜熱時咁遲"},{"pid":"f559ab87214f00578467f3ff7e9ef473a581f219","tid":275521,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}